        Graphics.Gloss.Internals.Interface.Backend.GLUT

  If flag(GLFW)
    Build-Depends:
        GLFW-b >= 0.1.0.1 && < 0.2
    CPP-Options: -DWITHGLFW
    Other-modules:
        Graphics.Gloss.Internals.Interface.Backend.GLFW



